猫王埃尔维斯·普雷斯利 (Elvis Presley) 的蓝色绒面革鞋在拍卖会上拍出高价https://www.nme.com/news/music/elvis-presleys-blue-suede-shoes-sell-for-huge-amount-at-auction-3771447?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=elvis-presleys-blue-麂皮鞋在拍卖会上拍出高价Adam EnglandTue, 02 Jul 2024 14:52:30 +0000 Music NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3771447 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Elvis-Presley.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="埃尔维斯·普雷斯利表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Elvis-Presley.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Elvis-Presley-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Elvis-Presley-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Elvis-Presley-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Elvis-Presley-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Elvis-Presley-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这双标志性鞋款售价高达 12 万英镑</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/elvis-presleys-blue-suede-shoes-sell-for-huge-amount-at-auction-3771447">埃尔维斯·普雷斯利 (Elvis Presley) 的蓝色麂皮鞋在拍卖会上拍出高价的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Elvis-Presley.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="埃尔维斯·普雷斯利表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Elvis-Presley.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Elvis-Presley-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Elvis-Presley-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Elvis-Presley-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Elvis-Presley-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Elvis-Presley-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/elvis-presley">猫王</a>本人穿过的一双蓝色麂皮鞋在拍卖会上拍出了天价。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-interviews/sofia-coppola-elvis-presley-priscilla-villain-3565087">索菲亚·科波拉在《普里西拉》中揭露埃尔维斯丑陋的一面：“我从来不想让他成为恶棍”</a></strong></li></ul><p> 6 月 28 日，这双鞋在迪韦齐斯的拍卖行<a href="https://bid.henryaldridge.com/past-auctions/henry-10055/lot-details/b42760e8-9cb8-40f5-8ced-b19601504259" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Henry Aldrige &amp; Son</a>中以 12 万英镑的价格售出——这是他们预计售价 10 万至 12 万英镑的最高价。</p><p>普雷斯利 (Presley) 在表演卡尔·珀金斯 (Carl Perkins) 的热门歌曲《蓝色麂皮鞋》(Blue Suede Shoes) 后首次购买了这双鞋，并在整个 20 世纪 50 年代穿着这双鞋参加各种采访和公开露面，其中最著名的是在美国的史蒂夫·艾伦秀 (The Steve Allen Show) 上，他在节目中表演了《猎犬》(Hound Dog) &#39;。</p><p> 20 世纪 50 年代末，当普雷斯利应征入伍时，他将这双鞋送给了一位朋友。</p><p>正如拍卖师安德鲁·奥尔德里奇所说，这双鞋是“当你谈论埃尔维斯·普雷斯利时你立即想到的”，它们“超越了流行文化”。</p><p>他补充道：“当埃尔维斯加入美国军队时，他在格雷斯兰举行了一次聚会。埃尔维斯把其中一些人叫到楼上，并赠送了一些他从军队回来后认为自己不需要或不想要的衣服。这位先生是艾伦·福塔斯 (Alan Fortas)，他是埃尔维斯的分行经理，也是他的朋友。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C8q0tA6ovoA/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 a